OL,3,CPolicy 2024: Knife crime is top of the
OL,4,Cagenda for parties' law and order
OL,5,Cpolicy
OL,7,FITV News Social Affairs Correspondent
OL,8,FSarah Corker looks at how the
OL,9,Fpolitical parties have said they will
OL,10,Ftackle law and order in their
OL,11,Fmanifestos
OL,13,FHistorically, the Conservatives have
OL,14,Fpositioned themselves as the party of
OL,15,Flaw and order - tough on crime.
OL,16,FPartygate eroded that brand.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
