OL,5,Cpolicy
OL,7,FA clear indication that recent high
OL,8,Fprofile scandals within various police
OL,9,Fforces - from appalling acts of
OL,10,Fmisconduct to huge failures in vetting
OL,11,Fprocedures - has had a devastating
OL,12,Feffect on public attitudes and
OL,13,Fperceptions towards those who are
OL,14,Fsupposed to keep us all safe.
OL,16,FWhat does the crime data tell us?
