OL,3,CPolicy 2024: Knife crime is top of the
OL,4,Cagenda for parties' law and order
OL,5,Cpolicy
OL,7,FStatistics on offending rates can be a
OL,8,Fdisputed area with politicians picking
OL,9,Fand choosing snapshots which suit
OL,10,Ftheir narratives - but arguably the
OL,11,Fmost reliable source of data comes
OL,12,Ffrom the ONS Crime Survey for England
OL,13,Fand Wales.
OL,15,FIn 2023, there was a 7% increase in
OL,16,Fknife crime compared to the year
OL,17,Fbefore, with nearly 50,000 offences.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
