OL,3,CPolicy 2024: Knife crime is top of the
OL,4,Cagenda for parties' law and order
OL,5,Cpolicy
OL,7,FOffending is concentrated in urban
OL,8,Fareas. Together the Metropolitan
OL,9,FPolice Force, (29% of all knife crime
OL,10,Foffences) and West Midlands Police
OL,11,F(11%) account for close to half of all
OL,12,Frecorded knife crime.
OL,14,FNotable increases were seen in the
OL,15,Fnumber of knife robberies in England
OL,16,Fand Wales - up 20% compared with the
OL,17,Fprevious year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
