OL,7,FWhile the Lib Dems would take a public
OL,8,Fhealth approach to tackling violent
OL,9,Fcrime with early intervention.
OL,11,FSentencing reform
OL,13,FThere are plenty of pledges for
OL,14,Ftougher sentences for a range of
OL,15,Fcrimes.
OL,17,FOne specific commitment in the
OL,18,FConservative manifesto is a promise to
OL,19,Fincrease sentences for domestic
OL,20,Fmurderers to a minimum jail term of 25
OL,21,Fyears.
