OL,7,FLabour didn't go as far as the Tories,
OL,8,Fbut promised a full review of the
OL,9,Fsentencing system.
OL,11,FJulie Devey's daughter, Poppy, was 24
OL,12,Fwhen she was murdered by her ex-
OL,13,Fboyfriend at their flat in 2018. He
OL,14,Finflicted more than 70 knife and stab
OL,15,Fwounds on Poppy using a kitchen knife.
OL,16,FHer killer was jailed for a minimum of
OL,17,F16 years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/19
