OL,7,FBecause the knife he used was already
OL,8,Fin the home ` the minimum tariff is 15
OL,9,Fyears in prison. Had Poppy been
OL,10,Fstabbed in the street with a knife
OL,11,Ftaken to the scene, the starting point
OL,12,Fwould be 25 years. It's a ten year
OL,13,Fdifference that the Conservative said
OL,14,Fthey will change.
OL,16,FMs Devey welcomes the political focus
OL,17,Fon sentencing but said the pledges
OL,18,Fdon't go far enough. She told ITV News
OL,19,F"Enough is enough. These domestic
OL,20,Fkillers need locking up for longer."
