OL,5,Cpolicy
OL,7,FThe Tories would recruit 8,000 more
OL,8,Ffull time police officers over three
OL,9,Fyears. Labour have promised to
OL,10,Fdedicate 13,000 police officers to
OL,11,Ftackling neighbourhood crime, although
OL,12,Fnot all of those would be full time
OL,13,Fpositions.
OL,15,FThe Lib Dems haven't set a target, but
OL,16,Fsaid they'd focus on community
OL,17,Fpolicing and recruiting more
OL,18,Fdetectives. Reform UK want 40,000 new
OL,19,Fpolice officers over the next five
OL,20,Fyears.
